      • addInterval

        public void addInterval(Interval i)
        Insert a new tuple in ascending order to the Interval set. If the tuple intersects another tuple, a new tuple will be generated and replace the existing tuple.
        Parameters:
        i - new tuple to insert.
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if a tuple with the same min and max exists or if the interval passed is null.
